    - Import .ttf/.otf back into an editable template
    - Pen/stylus pressure (Windows Ink) baked into glyphs and exported font
    - Live pangram preview; per-range export; system-font fallback for missing glyphs
    
    Notes
    - Folders/categories in sidebar, Home with recently-opened + favorites strips
    - Search, tags, drag-and-drop ordering, sort modes
    - Per-note font binding, rotating backups + atomic save, per-note undo
